			Winter Bess (pt_BR), Andrey Fedoseev (ru), Alexander
			Toresson (sv)
- New translations: Alexander Nyakhaychyk (be), Geraint Rowlands (cy), Tome
                    Boshevski (mk), A S Alam (pa)


